          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1934.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Drain your <strong>tuna</strong></p>",
