    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza bases</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> between the<strong> pizza bases </strong>and spread it evenly all over them</p><p>Top the pizzas with the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong>, <strong>drained tuna</strong>, <strong>halved olives</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong></p>",
